			<p>One of the pledges we made in the Kickstarter campaign was to be transparent with the finances for this project. Six months after we received the funds and with the camera nearly ready, let's have a look at where the money's gone.</p>
<p>First the build of the camera itself, then the accounts for the project as a whole.</p>
